title: Rishi Sunak’s AI Guest List Struggles to Secure World Leaders’ Presence
description: In a race against time, Prime Minister Rishi Sunak finds himself grappling with a less-than-stellar guest list for his upcoming AI summit, scheduled for November 1-2 at Bletchley Park.
